description: This data represents the six Townships within Salt Lake County.  The Copperton and Emigration Townships were voted on and passed in the 1996 election.  The Magna Township was passed by the Salt Lake County Council on Aug 21, 2001, Effective date: Oct. 1, 2001.  The Kearns Township was passed by the Salt Lake County Council on April 2, 2002, Effective date: June 1, 2002. The Millcreek Township was passed by the Salt Lake County Council on Oct 8, 2002, Effective date: Oct. 23, 2002. The White City Township was passed by The Salt Lake County Council on Sept 26,2006 Effective date: Sept. 26, 2006.
